Comment: 0,0:01:31.02,0:01:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(OP)
Comment: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you're from Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a boring place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the food there sure is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are lots of beautiful gals too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been half a year since the truce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.39,0:02:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just be glad we've managed to survive in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I win again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you win again?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.36,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey missy, you awake there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your share of the winnings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for giving me such an expensive gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. They say if we treat the bugler nicely,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be able to hear the calls for retreat loud and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, there's no conscription anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's rare to see a new recruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! It's because I wanted to learn music.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard, missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Private Second Class, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:14.54,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kono sora no kagayaki kimi no mune ni todoiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.76,0:00:14.54,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The luminance of the sky has reached your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:24.57,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}yumemiteta shirabe wa shizukesa no youni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:24.57,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}The melody I dreamed of was like silence.
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.44,0:00:29.62,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no te ga mada yume ni tookutemo
Dialogue: 1,0:00:24.44,0:00:29.62,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even if your hand is still far away in my dreams,
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.68,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}omoidashiteyou yasashii koe wo
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.68,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}I'll still remember your kind voice
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.44,0:00:47.47,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}dareka ga kimi no tame utatta shiawase no koto
Dialogue: 3,0:00:34.44,0:00:47.47,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and the happiness that was sung for you.
Dialogue: 4,0:00:47.21,0:00:56.87,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}sora no woto hibike takaku kanashimi wo koete
Dialogue: 4,0:00:47.21,0:00:56.87,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Let the sound of the sky ring high over your sadness.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.64,0:01:07.42,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}kimi no me ni utsuru mono wa subete hontou no sekai
Dialogue: 5,0:00:56.64,0:01:07.42,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything reflected in your eyes is that of the real world.
Dialogue: 6,0:01:07.25,0:01:16.89,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}namida sae kimi wo koko ni todomete okenai
Dialogue: 6,0:01:07.25,0:01:16.89,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Even tears won't be able to stop you here.
Dialogue: 7,0:01:16.62,0:01:29.02,OPR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}furisosogu hikari no naka ashita wo kanadete
Dialogue: 7,0:01:16.62,0:01:29.02,OPE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Amidst the descending lights, you'll play the song of tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:21.31,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,138)}The Resounding Sound{might as well stay consistent with the rest of the ep and use "resonate" instead of "resound" - Sounds great}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:21.31,Titles,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,621)}The Town of Dawn{This is correct, possessive}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize is having a festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is as far as I can take you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is your newly assigned post.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.19,0:05:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's commonly known as the Time-Trumpeting Fort.{Ok, so I like this title, only because of it's double-meaning. Plus Trumpeting = Announcing/Heralding/Telling/etc. If you don't like it... we can still go with "The Time-Heralding/Telling/Keeping Fort" I guess...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are to go there yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Notice of Appointment for Private Second Class Sorami Kanata:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.77,0:06:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are hereby assigned to the 1121st Platoon stationed in Seize, Trois State.{Makes no sense for Trois State to be in front of Seize when a couple of lines down, Konata calls it a town.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As ordered by the Republic of Helvetia's Central Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission accomplished at 1320!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous town of water and glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to report in at 1500.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll finally be able to make you sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming direction... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming time... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Confirming equipment... Check!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...march!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-flat... What a beautiful sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10.25 yen. {10 yen, 25 sen equates to this}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a pretty doll—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A kitten who was too engrossed in the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ran full speed in some random direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kittens do like to run around aimlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.91,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes them cute, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if it's just a stray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, this was a house cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.44,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That really surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.42,0:09:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was able to find something else wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's a soldier! Are you from the fort?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.82,0:09:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for protecting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sprayed me earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And... open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:09:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot or something?!{Ok... i just have to keep it. I like this >_> - I agree-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.34,0:10:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually getting involved... {Fixed-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do looking like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.78,0:10:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.58,0:11:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really was an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't you even dodge?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. This kind of dye disappears on its own once you dry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the festival event, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from a legend in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Flame Maidens who protected this town. { or maidens, or "protect" jajajaja}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for troubling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems the repairs are finished as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That meddlesome girl...{ok... "Felicia" should be a girl's name you know... >_>}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late! She's so late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so freaking late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.78,0:12:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we came all the way here just to welcome her too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But let's continue to wait, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a gift from your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.26,0:12:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done. Thank you very much for your hospitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but I'm always getting lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to that, I was able to meet such wonderful people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't get lost out here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can recognize notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very clear and yet somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...very nostalgic sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't what I—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to throw your life away for that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. It's probably meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to do so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was precious to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.50,0:14:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward march!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.15,0:14:57.74,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Do you want to see things developed by your voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.95,0:15:04.96,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Do you want to see a purer air, a world with the changed hearts of men?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:12.09,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}But everything on the Earth is fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:18.89,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Nothing is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:37.03,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}When all is said and done, reality is not always mirrored in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Flame Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very long time ago...
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.82,0:15:44.04,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Which to others, see horrid and demonic things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a story from before the world became the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep within the bowels of the town,
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.87,0:15:49.54,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}No matter whose story you hear,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,dwelt a winged demon.
Dialogue: 3,0:15:49.33,0:15:56.63,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}only your eyes can tell the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That demon spewed flames that made the ground tremble,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:05.31,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}We'll sing the world's colors
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and caused the people to suffer greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.47,0:16:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, the demon snatched up all the maidens that lived in the fort,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:12.73,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}and not forget a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.31,0:16:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and imprisoned them within an underground labyrinth.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.52,0:16:18.95,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything has a reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the maidens did not give up.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.74,0:16:29.12,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}like the stars in the symphony of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.62,0:16:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the heavenly gift they had received, they called upon each other with the a golden horn...{I think it makes sense to be plural here, i.e. multiple Golden Horns. TLC can check >_> - Certainly makes more sense in English-N}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and finally escaped the labyrinth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.12,0:16:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the aid of a giant spider,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they defeated the demon and beheaded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.71,0:16:40.97,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everyone makes a song of the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the head continued to spew flames.
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.76,0:16:48.02,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Everything is taught and bound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing was done,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the village below would soon turn to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to stop the flames,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:47.85,0:16:54.19,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}When we see each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the maidens took turns embracing the demon's head.
Dialogue: 3,0:16:53.98,0:17:01.36,InsE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}we'll become one with the stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the demon's head continued to blaze in the maidens' arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.36,0:17:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the villagers doused them both with water every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went on for an entire year,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until the flame finally died out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henceforth,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to thank the maidens in Heaven who had sacrificed their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Water-Dousing Festival came to be.{Ok, she says "matsuri", which is festival, and I think she's referring to the festival itself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the new girl didn't show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander, hurry up and look! It's Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really suits her well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Giving her this job was indeed a good decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we draw lots to—{they weren't exactly straws. the proper phrase is "lots" although i hope people understand that one... otherwise we could go back to "straws"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got lost again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to have fun when I got lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was because I was able to meet some nice strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see my mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish for it from the bottom of your heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your thoughts will definitely reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.08,0:19:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.25,0:19:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sound will resound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it will resound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be conveyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May the Flame Maidens here be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embracing the demon and nullifying its curse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they offered themselves, so that the demon would never awaken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of a golden horn...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.78,0:19:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the demon has awakened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.88,0:20:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... let my sound... reach someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reached.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.11,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resounds... and will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and wake up! Private Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where am I?{Japanese say "this place is", English say "Where am I"... meh....}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When are you going to wake up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Time-Trumpeting Fort,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the post of the 1121st Platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.98,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday... um... Sorry for causing you trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.53,0:21:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't endanger yourself like that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing all that for this stupid bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.48,0:21:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.94,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why this place is known as the Time-Trumpeting Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sound of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.44,0:23:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.61,0:23:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you how to be a good bugler.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.74,0:23:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Sergeant Major Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.70,0:23:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Filicia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.71,0:23:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Commander's desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't go by rank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.96,0:23:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.72,0:23:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's start right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.93,0:23:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play me a morning call right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.24,0:24:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl this time seems to be very lacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:17.38,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's remember our love and friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.29,0:24:17.38,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou omoikasanete
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.26,0:24:20.59,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}and play out their importance.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:17.26,0:24:20.59,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}taisetsu wo kanadeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.53,0:24:38.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}We were so happy that we cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.53,0:24:38.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}ureshikute naita
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.49,0:24:44.53,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}It hurt so much that we laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.49,0:24:44.53,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}itakute waratta
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:53.71,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}But these are all proof that we are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.58,0:24:53.71,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}dakedo sonna zenbu ga ikiteru akashi nan desu
Dialogue: 1,0:24:53.42,0:24:58.05,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let's move forward one step at a time.
Dialogue: 1,0:24:53.42,0:24:58.05,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}yukkuri aruite yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.55,0:24:59.51,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Everybody singing
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.38,0:25:04.01,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Let me hear the words of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.38,0:25:04.01,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}hitosashi no honne kikasete
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.47,0:25:05.22,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.01,0:25:10.89,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Even if our love and friendship sometimes waver,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.01,0:25:10.89,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}aijou yuujou toki ni yuretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.02,0:25:11.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}I know, you know, a little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:16.82,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}let's make it echo forever and ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:16.82,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}zutto zutto hibiki aitai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:17.19,EDRE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.90,0:25:23.16,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Words are hardly enough to describe it.
Dialogue: 1,0:25:16.90,0:25:23.16,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}arifureteru kotoba de wa tsutaekirenai
Dialogue: 1,0:25:22.86,0:25:28.95,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}This is our harmony.
Dialogue: 2,0:25:22.86,0:25:28.95,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}watashitachi no harmony
Dialogue: 2,0:25:28.87,0:25:34.00,EDE,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}Can you hear it? Our harmony!
Dialogue: 3,0:25:28.87,0:25:34.00,EDR,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(240,300)}kikoeru our harmony
